name: YETI
description: Long ago, deep within the swampy wetlands of the meme multiverse, one amphibian were born under very different stars. One would go on to become a global icon, forever etched into internet history. $YETI was the golden child—cold-rich, cute, and effortlessly Yeti isn’t just a brand; it’s a movement. Optimistic by Nature: Yeti sees the brighter side of the future and is determined to build it right.
